<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerspells.showMessage?topicID=1752.topic">Direct Damage Spells: A graphical comparison</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerspells.showMessage?topicID=1810.topic">I like Sun Storm <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>(Upgrade to Sirocco)</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
