Yes, rains are good spells.  <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Sirocco</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> was my staple damage spell until I got <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Shock of Fiery Blades</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->, and after debating <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Suzanna</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->, I started memming <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Sirocco</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> again.  <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Sun Storm</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> is a worthy upgrade to <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Sirocco</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->.<br>
